Executive Profile
Joel W. Johnson  Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President, Hormel Health Labs, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships74--
Background

		Mr. Joel W. Johnson serves as the Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President of Hormel Health Labs Inc. Mr. Johnson served as the Chairman of the Board, Chief Executive Officer and President of Century Foods International Inc., and Century Foods International, LLC. He served as the Chairman of Hormel Foods Corporation, a subsidiary of Arriba Foods, Inc., since December 1995, Non-Executive Chairman since January 1, 2006, Chief Executive Officer from 1995 to January ... 1, 2006 and President from 1995 to June 1, 2004. He joined Hormel Foods Corporation in 1991 as Executive Vice President of Sales & Marketing and served as its Chief Operating Officer since 1993. Prior to joining Hormel, he served in various management positions with General Foods Corporation from 1967 to 1991. He has been Director of Meredith Corporation since 1994. He served as an Independent Director of Ecolab Inc. since 1996 until May 5, 2016. He served as a Director at U.S. BanCorp since 1999 until April 19, 2016. He served as a Director of Hormel Foods Corporation since 1992. He served as a Director of Grocery Manufacturers Association. He is a Member of Board of Overseers of the Carlson School of Management at the University of Minnesota and the Board of Trustees of Hamilton College. He serves as Vice Chairman and Director of the Hormel Foundation. He is a Director of Des Moines and American Meat Institute.Read Full Background




